"{\"uid\": \"news18.com-olympics-paris-olympics-2024-swimmer-katie-ledecky-confirms-greatness-with-9th-gold-medal-8989533.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Already rated one of swimming's all-time greats coming into the Paris Olympics, Katie Ledecky made it official on Saturday by storming to victory in her signature event, the 800m freestyle to end her work in the French capital in grand style.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 80, \"end\": 93, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}, {\"begin\": 212, \"end\": 218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.6892338126296008, \"rank\": 0.40444531560227287, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French torpedo Leon Marchand may be the prince of Paris, electrifying the home nation with four spectacular gold medals.\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 244, \"end\": 250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.6892338126296008, \"rank\": 0.40444531560227287, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 264, \"end\": 272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.999999998583462, \"rank\": 1.375959614621718e-09, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}, {\"begin\": 294, \"end\": 299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999538431, \"rank\": 4.619678263405885e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it is Ledecky leaving Paris sharing the throne of greatest female Olympian with Larisa Latynina after winning a ninth gold medal to equal the Russian gymnast's record.\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 391, \"end\": 396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999538431, \"rank\": 4.619678263405885e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 435, \"end\": 443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999922241411155, \"rank\": 7.77591929708536e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larisa Latynina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\"}, {\"begin\": 511, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9815274906642824, \"rank\": 0.014205464963998255, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The week was kind of, you know, had its ups and downs like any other meet,\\\" said Ledecky, whose Paris haul also included gold in the 1,500, silver in the 4\\u00d7200 freestyle relay and bronze in the 400m free.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 639, \"end\": 644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999538431, \"rank\": 4.619678263405885e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew I just had to focus on the races, do not focus on times, just focus on getting the job done, getting to hear the national anthem at the end of the races as many times as I could,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 947, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In sharp contrast to Ledecky's runaway win in the 1,500m the 800m freestyle was a thriller from start to finish, with Ariarne Titmus matching her stroke-for-stroke for almost the entire distance.\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1067, \"end\": 1081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariarne Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But with the American setting a relentless, grinding pace her great Australian rival would never get her nose in front settling for silver with Ledecky getting to the wall first in a time of 8 minutes, 11.04 seconds.\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1361, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1213, \"end\": 1223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9994336122607141, \"rank\": 0.00043698064890882534, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew it was going to be a tough race.\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt confident but I knew it was going to be tough no matter what all the way to the finish.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have good early speed, and I can come home hard, and I can trust my endurance.\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew I just needed to stay calm through that and really just try to inch my way forward each lap, and I think I did a pretty good job of that,\\\" said Ledecky.\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It marked the fourth consecutive Games Ledecky has won the 800m free, and she joins compatriot Michael Phelps as the only swimmers to win gold in four different Olympics.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1836, \"end\": 1850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.123017270885476e-53, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Given that Michael's the only one that's ever done that, I think that just shows how difficult that is.\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 2021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Especially in the 800.\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2044, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just a lot of miles,\\\" said Ledecky.\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 800m was the final event on Ledecky's Paris card and she returns home having added two golds, a silver and a bronze, bringing her Olympic stockpile to 14 medals in all - with more possible.\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2129, \"end\": 2134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999538431, \"rank\": 4.619678263405885e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old admitted that a home Olympics in Los Angeles in four years' time intrigues her but she was not ready to commit to being there.\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2330, \"end\": 2341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999989398416964, \"rank\": 1.0498339338851321e-06, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swipe Left For Next Video  \\\"I'd love to.\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will see, I mean, it's not easy.\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Again, I will take it year by year, and we will see, give it everything I have got for as long as I have left in me,\\\" said Ledecky.\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CatchParis Olympics 2024 Day 8 LIVE UpdatesHere.\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2683, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay updated with the latest fromOlympics 2024.\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ExploreIndia At Paris Olympics 2024 Today.\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Check the updated list ofParis Olympics 2024 Medal Tally.\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CheckParis Olympics 2024 Event Results.\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Latest Blogs\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2886, \"entities\": []}]}"